<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.6">
<l>kōḻi kūveṉṉumāl</l>
<l>tōḻinā ṉeṉceykēṉ</l>
<l>āḻi vaṇṇarva rumpoḻu tāyiṟṟu</l>
<l>kōḻi kūveṉṉumāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The rooster is crowing!</l>
<l>Dear friend, what do I do?</l>
<l>The time the sea-hued one would come is past.</l>
<l>The rooster is crowing!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
